    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Women's suits consisting of trousers and a matching top in the form of a jacket, tunic or the like.  May also have a matching blouse or belt.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
